title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a highlight or map, an exception is thrown.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data from a table that contains a highlight or map.
SR: Steps to Reproduce: 1. Open the attached report. 2. Navigate to the table that contains a highlight or map. 3. Attempt to export the data from the table. Verify that an exception is thrown.
